This test will check that Kolourpaint can draw an image
<dl>
    <dt>Launch kolourpaint</dt>
        <dd>kolourpaint opens and showing one window by default</dd>
    <dt>Click on 'Pen(P)' button in the leftside of the window</dt>
        <dd>Draw anything in the drawing area</dd>
    <!-- EAGER STEP -->    
    <dt>Click on 'Save' > Enter the name of the file > Click on 'Save' button in the 'Save Image' dialogue box</dt>
        <dd>The image is saved</dd>
</dl>

